\id 2PE DunXian: DunXian Bible draft 2 
\h Beduru Huaisan Ji 2 Hui Xin 
\toc1 Beduru Huaisan Ji 2 Hui Xin 
\toc2 2Beduru 
\toc3 2Bed 
\mt1 Beduru Huaisan Ji 2 Hui Xin 
\c 1  
\s1 Kielien Asazho 
\p  
\v 1 \pn Ersa\pn* Mexihade hoji, shitu danlasan \pn Ximun-Beduru\pn* mai Huda, jiuichen \pn Ersa\pn* Mexihai gundanni tungo giezhi bijien mutun zhiguitu xianxin gieku bisan kunlade xin huaizho.  
\v 2 Nenjien, pinnan Huda, mai Ezhan \pn Ersa\pn*ni tanikui tungo giezhi tande olon ire gie! 
\s1 Huda Uruzhi Sunghusan Kunla 
\p  
\v 3 Huda tebieji nenlighalane matan xienliande udu daokude keresanlai man ogizho. Goya famatu, gounighalane mai urusan hhei tanikughala ingiezho.  
\v 4 Enezighanyi tungo giezhi Huda zhiguitu, fugie dainni matande ogizho. Ingiedene nefuxinse iresan duyani qida olukuse tai likai gieghazhi Hudai tejiende hhantulaghazho.  
\v 5 Zhen ene yenyinde oluzhi ta xiacha giezhi xianxin gieku jiere gounii, gouni jiere erlini,  
\v 6 erlin jiere goyane kunzhi giekui, goyane kunzhi gieku jiere rennaini, rennai jiere xienliantui,  
\v 7 xienliantu jiere gaijiulade orekui, gaijiulade oreku jiere kunlade orekui olodogha.  
\v 8 Enela tande bizhi olodose mai Ezhan \pn Ersa\pn* Mexihani taniku jiere tai yama oronde wizhi xiogo witui ulie gholughane.  
\v 9 Kunde ene giedun uwoshi zinie chadashikui chanlazhi gholoshikui chanla dane, sugho niekielien wo. Daosan zuinini arughasei matazho.  
\v 10 Ingiese gaijiula, ta genjia xiacha giezhi Huda tai urusan, sunghusanyi khidunde gholugha. Ta enei giese ulie furane.  
\v 11 Ingiezhi giese mai Ezhan, yeshijiu jiuichen \pn Ersa\pn* Mexihani chanqiku gojiade sunfande orone. 
\p  
\v 12 Ta ijin enelai mejiezhi ede bisan zhendao jiere khidunde beizho, ingieliuzhe bi enelai chan tande jilaghaye.  
\v 13 Bi sumulase bi amitu xienzide enelai tande jila ireghase indanji wo.  
\v 14 Mai Ezhan \pn Ersa\pn* Mexiha made mejieghasan mutun mii shihou oloncha widakui bi mejiene.  
\v 15 Bi duya ijiedene ene shiqinlai tai chan jilaghane giezhi bi jinlianji xiacha giene. 
\s1 Mexihani Famai Bijien Chujieghewo 
\p  
\v 16 Bijien mai Ezhan \pn Ersa\pn* Mexihani fugie nenli, hhe ireku shiqinlai tande kieliekushi goude bienjisan yama genzi witu guhualai ese daghazho. Bijien hhei famatui qinsi uzhezhi daozho.  
\v 17 Zui famatu hhense shenqi irezhi "Eneshi bi oresan mii kewon wo, bi hhende xiqi wo." giezhi hhende kieliekude hhe ada Hudase zhigui, famani jienliewo.  
\v 18 Bijien hhere zhiguitu ulade bikude ene shenqi asiman jierese iresanyi qinsi sonosuwo. 
\p  
\v 19 Matande pse xienzhila melie kieliesan genjia kekaotu kielien wine. Ta hhei zhuyi giese oluzho. Hheshi kharanide zhouisan zhula niekielien wo, ogheizhi eqiemaghaku hodun tai zhughede khizhetula zhouine.  
\v 20 Ta mejieku zui zhunyonishi ene wo, jinwun jieredu soyuji melie kieliesan kielienlai goyane isighala jieshi giese ulie olune.  
\v 21 Melie kieliesan kielienshi kunni isighala kieliesan pusho, Shenlin kunni zhughei gojiolughadene Hudai isii kielieghazho. 
\c 2  
\s1 Jia Loushi 
\p  
\v 1 Eqighandei bexinlai dunda jia xienzhila khizhesan mutun jianlai tai dundaye jia loushila khizhene. Hhela ghulazhi kunni widaghaku daolini ireghane. Hhela goyai shuisan Ezhanni ulie renjizhi widakude holune.  
\v 2 Ingieliuzhe olon kunla hhela lon kijiezhi hu giesanyi daghane. Hhelai yenyinghala zhendaoni sugiene.  
\v 3 Hhela tanxin giezhi ghudanghala tai jierese haochu ereine giezho. Huda hhelade eqighanse zui jinjizho, hhelai widaghakui danwu ulie giene. 
\p  
\v 4 Huda zui fanjisan qienxienlai ese rouliedene dozoheini khara nokiende bendazhi panjikui sagheighazho.  
\v 5 Pse eqighanku duyani ese rouliedene xienlian witu kunlai duyade hunshui ireghazhi zinie gundanni chonjisan \pn Nuhha\pn*ni nie gie neiman kunyi feilieghawo.  
\v 6 Pse \png Sodoma\png*, \png Emola\png* ghua chenshide zui jinjidene sideragha funiesun gholughazhi 1 houku xienlian witu kunlade jingao giezho.  
\v 7 Zinie mouxien kunla hu giesande yuchou giesan gou kun \pn Lutei\pn*ni jiuiwo.  
\v 8 Hhe gou kun hhelai dunda niudunie souzhi hhela giesan mouxiennilai chanlazhi sonosuse hhei gou zhugheni otuzho.  
\v 9 Ingiese Ezhan xienliantu kunyi shiikuse matugie jiuizhi gou witu kunyi feilieghadene panjiku udude faikui mejiene.  
\v 10 Tebieshi beyeni zannan nefuxinni daghasan kunla, pse qienlini yamacha ulie teisan kunlai genjia ingiene. 
\p Hhela jionaoghazhi goyane fugiede uzhezhi asiman jieredu famatulase ulie ayidene sugienema,  
\v 11 qienxienliuzhe fugie lilian, nenli bidene sugieku kielienghala Ezhanyi melie asiman jieredu famatulai ulie zhane.  
\v 12 Enezighan jia loushila olusanse alaku, yama sumula daku chushen mutun goya sugiesanne ulie mejiene, chushen mutun widane.  
\v 13 Hhela gou wini giedene goyai jiere gou wini ireghazho. Hhela udu hu giese bayasukui wo giezho. Tanre hhantu ijiekude piendakui giezhi bayasuzho. Hhelashi goujia, cheiqisan wo.  
\v 14 Hhela jin piofen giekui ereizho, ulie beidene zui fanjine. Bixin kunlai miine. Hhelai zhughede tanxin gieku gon oluwo. Hhelashi kharakui wo.  
\v 15 Hhela zhen moni bendadene \pn Bier\pn*ni kewon \pn Balan\pn*ni moni daghazhi xiemacha echiwo. \pn Balan\pn* zhendan witu baerde xiqi bidene  
\v 16 goya codasandene kheilaghawo. Enzheghe kielien kielie danema, kunni shenqighala kielien kieliezhi ene xienzhi fenjiulisei danlawo. 
\p  
\v 17 Enezighan kunlashi usu witu bula wo, honfen kei feiliesan u niekielien wo. Zui khara oronni hhelade zhunbei giezho.  
\v 18 Hhela yama oronde wiku fugie kielien kieliezhi hu gieku nefuxinghala hhezighan codasan shenhose jian likai giesan kunlai miizho.  
\v 19 Hhela kunlade ziyu ogine giezhi dain giezhoma, goyane qida olukude hoji danlazho. Kunni yan hanshiliese yande hoji danlazho.  
\v 20 Kunla mai Ezhan, yeshijiu jiuichen \pn Ersa\pn* Mexihai tanikughala duyani zannannise andadene zannanni pse hhelai jiohoro giezhi hanshiliese hhelai khuinashiku qinkon eqighankude ulie kurune.  
\v 21 Hhela zhen moni tanidene jienliesan zhiguitu minlinni bendase ulie mejiekuse da gou wo.  
\v 22 Kunla kieliesan kielien shuhua wo, hhelai jiere gholuwo, "Noghei kharei ire goya benzhesanne ijiene." "Wagha arughasan khighei pse shuwade ghoghoreine." 
\c 3  
\s1 Ersa Ireku Ghujinlazho 
\p  
\v 1 Mii orentula, eneshi bi tande huaisan ji 2 hui xin wo. Ene ghua xin dunda tai qixin giezhi loushi zhugheitai olodoghane giezho.  
\v 2 Zhiguitu xienzhila melie kieliesan kielienyi, pse tai shitulai tungo giezhi Ezhan, yeshijiu jiuichen ogisan minlinyi tai jila ireghane giezho.  
\v 3 Ta mejieku zui zhunyonishi ene wo, duya baraku xienzide uzhezhi xiniechen kunla khizhedene duranghalane giezhi uzhezhi xiniezhi  
\v 4 \pn "Ersa\pn* irene giezhi dain giesan khala wine? Mai xienrenla fugusanse eli kutula yanyanjila man wine, zui melieshida zhayaghasanghala niekielien wo." giezhi kieliene.  
\v 5 Hhela eqighandei Hudai kielienghala asimanni giesei, pse zemin ususe khizhezhi usughala gholusei nanxighan matazho.  
\v 6 Hhe shihouku duyani usughala manjidene widaghawoma,  
\v 7 edeku asiman, zeminni yen Hudai kielienghala feilieghazhi xienlian witu kunlai panjizhi widaghaku hhe udu kurune. Hhe shihoude asiman, zeminni khanghala tulie widaghane. 
\p  
\v 8 Mii orentula, enei ta bu mata, Ezhan uzhese niudushi 1000 nien wo, 1000 nienshi niudu wo.  
\v 9 Ezhan niezhan kunla sumulasan mutun dain giesanne danwu giezhi ulie chenjighakui pusho. Shijishan hhe tai rennai giezhi nieda ulie widaghadene jien kunlai geizhen gieghaku duran wo.  
\v 10 Ezhanni udu ghughei mutun irene. Hhe udude nie fugie shenqi irese asiman wida khine. Asiman jieredulai khanghala tulie widaghane. Zemin, zemin jiere giesanlai man widaghane.  
\v 11 Yanyanjila man ingie widase ta matunie kun danlane? Ta indan zhiguide, xienliande udu daokuni wo.  
\v 12 Hudai udui panjizhi ghujighan ire gie. Hhe udu kuzhese asimanyi khan tulie widaghane, asiman jieredulai tulie xiui widaghane.  
\v 13 Matan Huda dain giesan mutun gundanni durusan shini asiman, shini zeminni sagheizho. 
\p  
\v 14 Ingiese mii orentula, ta ene shiqinlai sagheise xiacha giezhi goyane bu zannanshighadene yama kheilakui wizhi Hudare heqishi.  
\v 15 Mai Ezhan rennai giekushi jiuiku jihui wo giezhi sumula. Zhen matan oresan gaijiu \pn Baolo\pn* zhao Huda hhende ogisan aghelighala tande xin huaisan mutun wo.  
\v 16 Hhei xinla jiere man enezighan shiqinlai kieliezho. Xin jiere niezhanlai dunjireku chijiashi erlin witu, undan witu kunla psedu jinwun mutun codazhi lijie giedene goyane widaghawo.  
\v 17 Ingiese mii orentula, ta enei eqighan mejiese goude xioxin gie. Pse mouxien kunlai codasan tai miidene goya undanlasan oronsene anda boune.  
\v 18 Ta mai Ezhan, yeshijiu jiuichen \pn Ersa\pn* Mexihani nenjien, taniku jiere henda. Kuaikui edese chanqi hhende ogi. Amine!